profile._text:
In 2011, Francesca embarked on her real estate journey, transitioning from a five-year tenure in the UK medical sector. Starting with rentals, she delved into the real estate industry, gradually shifting her focus to sales, luxury off-plan, and ready properties. Leveraging her extensive experience and a persona that resonates with ultra-high-net-worth clients, Francesca has thrived in her professional endeavors.

Recognized for her meticulous attention to detail and strong organizational acumen, Francesca remains committed to the pursuit of excellence and continuous growth. Interacting with a diverse clientele encompassing various backgrounds, nationalities, and social statuses over the years has further enriched her expertise.

With extensive knowledge spanning Dubai, Francesca's primary focus areas include, but are not limited to; Dubai Hills, Emirates Hills, Jumeirah Bay, and the Palm Jumeirah, as well as various other neighborhoods throughout the city. Her in-depth understanding of these locations has positioned her as a go-to expert for luxury property transactions all over Dubai.

Throughout her journey, Francesca has refined her skills and established herself as a respected and reliable luxury consultant, known for her strong referral network and commitment to delivering exceptional service. This dedication has solidified her reputation in the ever-evolving real estate market.

profile._text:
Active in the sales of upscale condominiums and investment projects since 1986 for both promoters and as a real estate agent, Phyllis has developed an enviable reputation as inspiring total confidence, being meticulous, calm and trustworthy.
